{"id":464,"date":"2020-09-22T13:23:50","date_gmt":"2020-09-22T13:23:50","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/?p=464"},"modified":"2020-09-22T13:23:52","modified_gmt":"2020-09-22T13:23:52","slug":"safety-protocols-to-follow-during-your-vacations-in-goa","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/safety-protocols-to-follow-during-your-vacations-in-goa\/","title":{"rendered":"Safety protocols to follow during your vacations in Goa"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Finally, the Goa border has opened welcoming tourists from across the country who were craving for a holiday all this while. Early July, the Goa government had announced the reopening of Goa borders for domestic tourism to get back the tourism industry running which has revived the hopes of getting Goan economy up.<br>No doubt staying at home has protected us from the deadly coronavirus, but as things are getting back to normal due to strict following of protocols, we can now plan to travel to the beautiful holiday destination, Goa.<br>But while you travel around in Goa, here are the safety protocols and measure laid down by Goa tourism department that every traveller need to follow.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Goa Tourism Guidelines<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Earlier travellers had to carry COVID negative certificates tested within the last two days, or they will have to go through a mandatory check on entering the state. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The ones who have been tested positive will either have to return back or quarantine in Goa itself till the further declaration of results.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Goa Tourism Departments has selected particular hotels, on which the travelers could get their pre-bookings done.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bookings in unapproved hotels will not be allowed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A self-declaration form must be filled up in the pre-booked hotel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Travelers with negative COVID certificates will not have to go through the Quarantine period.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tourists could enter the state through flights, trains which will stop only in particular stations like Madgaon, Thivim, and Vasco Da Gama or they might as well travel by road.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All the tourists will go through thermal screening at every entry point of the state.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tourists who decide on Quarantining in Goa based on their positive COVID certificate will have to isolate themselves for two weeks in institutional centers.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Finally, the Goa border has opened welcoming tourists from across the country who were craving for a holiday all this while. Early July, the Goa government had announced the reopening of Goa borders for domestic tourism to get back the tourism industry running which has revived the hopes of getting Goan economy up.No doubt staying [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":467,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/464"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=464"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/464\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":468,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/464\/revisions\/468"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/467"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=464"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"